==Pool==
Pools are constructed in upgrades: before a higher level pool can be built, the player must first build the one before it. The pool space will restore certain stats, depending on the type of pool built.

'''Note:''' You can use the [[crystal saw]] for an invisible +3 boost, combined with either [[Cup of tea (Player-owned house)|tea]] for a visible up to +3 boost (total boost +6), or a [[spicy stew]] for a visible up to +5 boost (total boost +8).

